      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like im just walking in circles lately. every time i think i finally figured things out, i just end up back at the exact same spot. another failed job, another breakup, another month of just feeling like nothing. it's like this heavy loop i can't get out of. i'm just so tired of starting over.",
