      "content": "therapists and friends.. i've tried all that. it's just the same advice every time. \"try harder,\" \"be patient,\" \"it gets better.\" but it doesnt. it's like a broken record. no matter what i do, the result is always the same. it feels less like a pattern i can fix and more like a fundamental flaw in me. i just feel like i'm running on a treadmill that's going nowhere.",
