      "content": "it just feels permanent. like no matter how many \"root causes\" i find, the loop stays. i look at my life and i just see this endless repetition of trying and failing and crashing. it's like i'm trapped in a room with no doors. sometimes it feels like the only way to actually stop the cycle and get some peace is to just... exit the loop entirely.",
